B.Qo=new A.T(B.ac,"ATIS delivers critical pre-flight information","ATIS (Automatic Terminal Information Service) broadcasts updated airport information continuously. Pilots must obtain the current ATIS information before contacting ATC and must confirm they have received it with the ATIS letter (Alpha, Bravo, Charlie\u2026).\n\nReading comprehension questions often use ATIS-style texts and ask you to extract specific information.",null,null,null)
