B.JO=new A.aE("The IRS requires an alignment period of approximately 10 minutes before departure.","IRS, kalk\u0131\u015ftan \xf6nce yakla\u015f\u0131k 10 dakikal\u0131k bir hizalama s\xfcresi gerektirir.","alignment period")
