B.R9=new A.T(B.ae,"\u2708\ufe0f Exam Tip",'Flight plan questions often focus on:\n\u2022 **Aircraft type / wake category** \u2014 know ICAO aircraft designators\n\u2022 **EET** (Estimated Elapsed Time) vs. **ETA** (Estimated Time of Arrival)\n\u2022 **Alternate airport** requirements \u2014 when is one required?\n\u2022 **PBN** (Performance Based Navigation) codes in Field 18\n\nCommon trick: "EOBT" = Estimated Off-Blocks Time (when pushback starts), NOT takeoff time.',null,null,null)
